{"tid":2083879,"cid":37,"subCid":13,"title":"［黃色經濟］原來驗樓、洗冷氣、簡單維修都有黃圈選擇 — 和你驗","createTime":"2020-06-29T04:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T10:05:28.000Z","uid":48083,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"faaf897d76e306316d0fcc5270556664177efd11","tid":2083879,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T04:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rDig8aZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDig8aZ.png&h=66d85d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/CheckWithYou/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FCheckWithYou%2F&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8WdKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=91b211a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/CheckWithYou/</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook<br />\n「和你驗」是一間社會企業，宗旨是以陪伴「踢保」、「保釋中」或因爭取公義社會導致經濟上有困難的年青人，好讓他們能保持生計同時具一定基本謀生技能。<br />\n<br />\n有別於傳統福利機構的援助，「和你驗」並不採取資源授與嘅方針；相反「和你驗」希望培養到他們一定技能。<br />\n<br />\n至今「和你驗」已與至少八名年青人共渡難關，其中一位更準備攻讀驗樓課程，我們希望未來這些年青人在「和你驗」畢業後，能在未來人生陪伴其他年青人共渡難關。<br />\n<br />\n創辦人Vin（化名）本身是一名驗樓師，大學期間修讀有關貧窮的社會政策，曾任區議員及立法會議員助理。2018年修畢由著名驗樓師主理之樓宇檢驗課程後，驗樓工作亦隨即起步，由丁屋到三萬元一尺的單位都有檢驗經驗。<br />\n<br />\n另一位拍檔是文師傅（化名），於冷氣工程工作逾10年，曾是具規模冷氣公司的東主，2019夏秋之交化整為零，專注社會公義，及後Vin和文師傅漸漸熟稔，決定合作，「和你驗」隨即誕生。<br />\n<br />\n「和你驗」得道多助，義務顧問團當中有兩位物業管理主任，一位曾任非政府非牟利的法定房屋機構任職，一位亦於全球房地產公司服務。他們都為新樓交收，驗收及執修等流程提供獨特見解及經驗分享，以協助「和你驗」在經濟的服務當中提供具競爭力的服務。<br />\n<br />\n由於「和你驗」兩位主理人非傳統工程公司出身，亦不追求榮華富貴。故希望以社會企業模式營運，同時部份服務項目的收費將回饋社會，爭取公義。"},{"pid":"c9c455d353a60747188987432ed190a23c2261a6","tid":2083879,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T04:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/krMB8km.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkrMB8km.png&h=ff7abf22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cuE4xM5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcuE4xM5.png&h=48595df8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ai8g8kt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fai8g8kt.png&h=565583b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dOLrL7a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdOLrL7a.png&h=661f0339&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qL5zayS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqL5zayS.png&h=51ff6323&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0909bdfa90427a78ab938352cfec49414219097","tid":2083879,"uid":67945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"080bb126ecb234b01772ee74726033c971a4513e","tid":2083879,"uid":337498,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:07:32.000Z","msg":"黃中帶綠，咪又係咁。"},{"pid":"fcd8e00585a30c082472c40e241e8d33dc107058","tid":2083879,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6911cbd7d7e918ed8a69e77e55b0b41f3cbfbd27","tid":2083879,"uid":75962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"080bb126ecb234b01772ee74726033c971a4513e","tid":2083879,"uid":337498,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:07:32.000Z","msg":"黃中帶綠，咪又係咁。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:41:21.000Z","msg":"bye 五毛"},{"pid":"fe60953710a25bd76b396c0fc1f1e19c1b8328ed","tid":2083879,"uid":59952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44b7093109dbfd714ad123a572fa9398424ba45","tid":2083879,"uid":19092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:47:48.000Z","msg":"牛角鎖手柄都有得捉唔水平， 屌你老母識唔撚識架？"},{"pid":"eb9b1ef10b08